  "product_overview": "Enhanced Telecom AI System 4.0 is a next-generation autonomous network intelligence platform that integrates Intent-Based Networking, Zero-Touch Automation, Quantum-Safe Security, Global Multi-Operator Federation, and Self-Evolving AI Agents. The system offers advanced AI-driven capabilities to optimize telecom network performance, security, and operational efficiency with comprehensive observability and automated agent evolution.",
  "core_goals": [
    "Enable high-level intent translation into automated network policies and enforcement with Intent-Based Networking (IBN).",
    "Automate deployments and updates securely with Zero-Touch Automation (ZTA) validated by Digital Twin simulations.",
    "Provide future-proof post-quantum cryptographic security ensuring secure communication and immutable audit logs.",
    "Facilitate global multi-operator coordination and federated learning for improved telecom network collaboration.",
    "Continuously optimize AI agents through automated machine learning, Neural Architecture Search (NAS), and hyperparameter tuning with Self-Evolving Agents.",
    "Offer comprehensive real-time monitoring and observability across all AI 4.0 features using Prometheus, Grafana, and MLflow."
  ],
  "key_features": [
    "Intent-Based Networking (IBN) for translating high-level user intents into network policies including QoS, routing, and MARL objectives.",
    "Zero-Touch Automation (ZTA) for fully automated deployment pipelines featuring rollback and digital twin validation.",
    "Quantum-Safe Security implementing post-quantum cryptography algorithms (CRYSTALS-Kyber, Dilithium) for secure communication and audit.",
    "Global Multi-Operator Federation enabling coordination, federated model sharing, encrypted communication, and cooperative telecom scenarios.",
    "Self-Evolving AI Agents leveraging AutoML, NAS, and continuous performance tracking and optimization.",
    "Real-time Dashboard with live data updates, WebSocket support, and detailed monitoring of system health and AI feature status.",
    "Comprehensive monitoring and metrics exposure with Prometheus and Grafana dashboards tailored for each AI 4.0 component.",
    "Robust Data Management API supporting real-time data ingestion and processing for telecom AI workloads."
  ],
  "user_flow_summary": [
    "User creates a high-level network intent via IBN API, system translates intent into actionable policies and monitors enforcement.",
    "Users initiate automated update pipelines for AI models and configurations via ZTA API; system conducts digital twin validation and orchestrates deployment with rollback capabilities.",
    "Operators join a global federation network, sharing and aggregating ML models securely; system coordinates cooperative scenarios like traffic spike simulations.",
    "Security administrators generate quantum-safe keys, encrypt/sign messages, and verify signatures ensuring future-proof communication.",
    "AI researchers create and execute self-evolution tasks to optimize agent architectures and performance, tracked via MLflow.",
    "Users monitor system and AI components in real-time dashboards, utilizing live updates and alerts on health metrics and AI statuses."
  ],
  "validation_criteria": [
    "Successful creation, enforcement, and monitoring of intents with no violations occurring under defined constraints.",
    "Zero-Touch Automation pipelines deploy updates safely, verified with digital twin validation and rollback executed correctly upon failures.",
    "Quantum-Safe Security key generation, encryption, signing, and verification processes function correctly for supported algorithms.",
    "Federation system allows multi-operator node joining, secure model sharing, and produces accurate cooperative scenario simulations.",
    "Self-Evolving Agent evolution tasks improve agent performance metrics as logged through MLflow.",
    "Real-time dashboards display accurate, up-to-date system metrics with WebSocket live data.",
    "Monitoring APIs reliably provide system health and performance metrics consistent with actual system state.",
    "Automated testing suites for IBN, ZTA, Quantum-Safe Security, Federation, and Self-Evolving features all pass consistently."
  ],
